news.title: 3 key takeaways from Nvidia's earnings: China blow, cloud strength and AI future
news.summary: The company's data center division continues to surge as companies, countries, and cloud providers snap up GPUs for artificial intelligence software. The company also continues to expand its cloud division.

news.title: Federal trade court strikes down Trump's reciprocal tariffs
news.summary: The Supreme Court could end up ruling if Trump has authority under the International Emergency Economic Powers Act to impose universal duties on imports. The case is expected to be heard by the end of the month.

news.title: United Airlines plans to return to JFK — again — in new partnership with JetBlue
news.summary: United and JetBlue announced a new partnership that will allow customers to earn and burn frequent flyer points on each other's airline. United and Jet Blue announced a partnership that allows customers to Earn and burn Frequent Flyer Points on Each other's Airline.

news.title: E.l.f. Beauty to acquire Hailey Bieber skincare brand Rhode in deal valued up to $1 billion
news.summary: E.l.f. Beauty is acquiring Hailey Bieber's skincare brand Rhode for up to $1 billion as it looks to reach higher-income shoppers.

news.title: Best Buy cuts full-year sales and profit guidance as tariffs raise cost of electronics
news.summary: Best Buy posted better-than-expected first-quarter earnings but cut its outlook. President Donald Trump's tariffs raise the cost of imported electronics.

news.title: CEO confidence registers sharpest fall-off in a half-century, new survey finds
news.summary: Chief executive confidence fell in the second quarter by the most in the nearly 50 years the poll has been conducted. A measure of chief executive confidence has fallen in the last three months.

news.title: Best Buy’s stock drops after it cuts profit outlook on tariff impact
news.summary: Best Buy predicts that tariffs will stay at current levels for the rest of the year. The company doesn't see a change in consumer behavior.

news.title: Nvidia results are proof the tech sector is worth investor loyalty, says strategist who recommended buying at April lows
news.summary: Ross Mayfield, investment strategist at Baird, says tech has been the ‘clearest opportunity’ in a year mired by politics.

news.title: Jobless claims jump to 5-week high — but not because layoffs in the U.S. are rising
news.summary: There’s little sign U.S. businesses are laying off more workers and preparing for bad times. Several months after the Trump White House triggered the biggest global trade wars in decades.

news.title: Economy shrank 0.2% in the first quarter, updated GDP shows, as trade wars sapped U.S. growth
news.summary: U.S. GDP seen partly rebounding in second quarter. China's economy expected to grow by 0.3% in the second quarter, up 0.4%.
